HEADWORD: Anthropocentric
<hw>An`thro*po*cen"tric</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>'a`nqrwpos</grk> man + <?/ center.]</ety> <def>Assuming man as the
center or ultimate end; -- applied to theories of the universe or of any
part of it, as the solar system.</def> <rj><au>Draper.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

